datasets.query:
WITH catalog_privileges AS (  
    SELECT *   
    FROM system.information_schema.catalog_privileges  
),  
distinct_catalog_privileges AS (  
    SELECT DISTINCT privilege_type  
    FROM catalog_privileges  
),  
privilege_catalog_types AS (  
    SELECT privilege_type  
    FROM distinct_catalog_privileges  
),  
pivoted_catalog_privileges AS (  
    SELECT   
        grantor,  
        'catalog' AS entity,
        grantee AS user,  
        catalog_name,  
        '' AS schema_name,
        '' AS table_name,
        '' AS volume_name,
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'ALL_PRIVILEGES' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS all_privileges,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'SELECT' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS select,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'MODIFY' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS modify,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'APPLY_TAG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS apply_tag,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_CATALOG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_catalog,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'REFRESH' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS refresh,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'EXECUTE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS execute,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_TABLE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_table,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MATERIALIZED_VIEW' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_materialized_view,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'BROWSE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS browse,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MODEL' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_model,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_FUNCTION' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_function,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'READ_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS read_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'WRITE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS write_volume  
    FROM catalog_privileges  
    GROUP BY grantor, grantee, catalog_name  
),
catalog_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,  
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.catalog_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name  
),

schema_privileges AS (  
    SELECT *   
    FROM system.information_schema.schema_privileges  
),  
distinct_schema_privileges AS (  
    SELECT DISTINCT privilege_type  
    FROM schema_privileges  
),  
privilege_schema_types AS (  
    SELECT privilege_type  
    FROM distinct_schema_privileges  
),  
pivoted_schema_privileges AS (  
    SELECT   
        grantor,  
        'schema' AS entity,
        grantee AS user,  
        catalog_name,  
        schema_name,
        '' AS table_name,
        '' AS volume_name,
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'ALL_PRIVILEGES' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS all_privileges,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'SELECT' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS select,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'MODIFY' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS modify,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'APPLY_TAG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS apply_tag,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_CATALOG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_catalog,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'REFRESH' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS refresh,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'EXECUTE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS execute,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_TABLE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_table,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MATERIALIZED_VIEW' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_materialized_view,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'BROWSE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS browse,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MODEL' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_model,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_FUNCTION' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_function,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'READ_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS read_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'WRITE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS write_volume  
    FROM schema_privileges  
    GROUP BY grantor, grantee, catalog_name, schema_name  
),
schema_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,  
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.schema_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name  
),

table_privileges AS (  
    SELECT *   
    FROM system.information_schema.table_privileges  
),  
distinct_table_privileges AS (  
    SELECT DISTINCT privilege_type  
    FROM table_privileges  
),  
privilege_table_types AS (  
    SELECT privilege_type  
    FROM distinct_table_privileges  
),  
pivoted_table_privileges AS (  
    SELECT   
        grantor,  
        'table' AS entity,
        grantee AS user,  
        table_catalog AS catalog_name,  
        table_schema AS schema_name,
        table_name AS table_name,
        '' AS volume_name,
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'ALL_PRIVILEGES' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS all_privileges,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'SELECT' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS select,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'MODIFY' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS modify,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'APPLY_TAG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS apply_tag,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_CATALOG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_catalog,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'REFRESH' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS refresh,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'EXECUTE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS execute,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_TABLE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_table,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MATERIALIZED_VIEW' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_materialized_view,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'BROWSE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS browse,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MODEL' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_model,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_FUNCTION' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_function,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'READ_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS read_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'WRITE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS write_volume  
    FROM table_privileges  
    GROUP BY grantor, grantee, table_catalog, table_schema, table_name
),
table_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,  
    table_name,
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.table_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name, table_name
), 

volume_privileges AS (  
    SELECT *   
    FROM system.information_schema.volume_privileges 
),  
distinct_volume_privileges AS (  
    SELECT DISTINCT privilege_type  
    FROM volume_privileges  
),  
privilege_volume_types AS (  
    SELECT privilege_type  
    FROM distinct_volume_privileges  
),  
pivoted_volume_privileges AS (  
    SELECT   
        grantor,  
        'volume' AS entity,
        grantee AS user,  
        volume_catalog AS catalog_name,  
        volume_schema AS schema_name,
        '' AS table_name,
        volume_name AS volume_name,
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'ALL_PRIVILEGES' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS all_privileges,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'SELECT' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS select,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'MODIFY' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS modify,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'APPLY_TAG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS apply_tag,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_CATALOG' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_catalog,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'USE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS use_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'REFRESH' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS refresh,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'EXECUTE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS execute,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_SCHEMA' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_schema,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_TABLE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_table,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MATERIALIZED_VIEW' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_materialized_view,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'BROWSE' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS browse,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_MODEL' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_model,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'CREATE_FUNCTION' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS create_function,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'READ_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS read_volume,  
        MAX(CASE WHEN privilege_type = 'WRITE_VOLUME' THEN 'Yes' ELSE '' END) AS write_volume  
    FROM volume_privileges  
    GROUP BY grantor, grantee, volume_catalog, volume_schema, volume_name
),
volume_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    volume_name,  
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.volume_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name, volume_name
),

union_dataset AS (
SELECT 
  c.*,   
  IFNULL(ct.tags, '') AS tags 
FROM 
  pivoted_catalog_privileges c
LEFT JOIN   
  catalog_tags ct  
ON   
  c.catalog_name = ct.catalog_name

UNION ALL

SELECT 
  s.*,   
  IFNULL(st.tags, '') AS tags 
FROM 
  pivoted_schema_privileges s
LEFT JOIN   
  schema_tags st  
ON   
  s.catalog_name = st.catalog_name AND s.schema_name = st.schema_name

UNION ALL 

SELECT  
  t.*,   
  IFNULL(tt.tags, '') AS tags 
FROM 
  pivoted_table_privileges t
LEFT JOIN   
  table_tags tt  
ON   
  t.catalog_name = tt.catalog_name AND t.schema_name = tt.schema_name AND t.table_name = tt.table_name

UNION ALL 

SELECT
  v.*,   
  IFNULL(vt.tags, '') AS tags 
FROM 
  pivoted_volume_privileges v
LEFT JOIN   
  volume_tags vt  
ON   
  v.catalog_name = vt.catalog_name AND v.schema_name = vt.schema_name AND v.volume_name = vt.volume_name)

SELECT 
    grantor AS `Grantor`, 
    user AS `User`, 
    entity AS `Entity`,
    catalog_name AS `Catalog name`,
    schema_name AS `Schema name`,
    table_name AS `Table name`,
    volume_name AS `Volume name`,
    tags AS `Tags`,
    all_privileges AS `All privileges`,
    select AS `Select`,
    modify AS `Modify`,
    apply_tag AS `Apply tag`,
    use_catalog AS `Use catalog`,
    use_schema AS `Use Schema`,
    refresh AS `Refresh`,
    execute AS `Execute`,
    create_schema AS `Create schema`,
    create_table AS `Create table`,
    create_materialized_view AS `Create materialized view`,
    browse AS `Browse`,
    create_model AS `Create model`,
    create_volume AS `Create volume`,
    create_function AS `Create function`,
    read_volume AS `Read volume`,
    write_volume AS `Write volume` 
FROM
    union_dataset

WHERE catalog_name != '__databricks_internal'
AND IF(:param_entity='<ALL>', true, entity = :param_entity)
AND IF(:param_catalog_name='<ALL>', true, catalog_name = :param_catalog_name) 
AND IF(:param_schema_name='<ALL>', true, schema_name = :param_schema_name)
AND IF(:param_table_name='<ALL>', true, table_name = :param_table_name)
AND IF(:param_volume_name='<ALL>', true, volume_name = :param_volume_name)

datasets.query:
WITH catalogs AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,  
    catalog_owner AS owner,  
    comment,
    last_altered,
    last_altered_by,
    created,
    created_by,
    'catalog' AS entity,  
    '' AS schema_name,  
    '' AS table_name,  
    '' AS volume_name,  
    '' AS data_source_format,  
    '' AS table_type  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.catalogs  
),  
catalog_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,  
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.catalog_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name  
),

schemas AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,  
    schema_owner AS owner,  
    comment,
    last_altered,
    last_altered_by,
    created,
    created_by,
    'schema' AS entity,  
    schema_name,  
    '' AS table_name,  
    '' AS volume_name,  
    '' AS data_source_format,  
    '' AS table_type  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.schemata
),  
schema_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,  
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.schema_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name  
),
tables AS (  
  SELECT   
    table_catalog AS catalog_name,  
    table_owner AS owner,  
    comment,
    last_altered,
    last_altered_by,
    created,
    created_by,
    'table' AS entity,  
    table_schema AS schema_name,  
    table_name,  
    '' AS volume_name,  
    data_source_format,  
    table_type  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.tables
),  
table_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,  
    table_name,
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.table_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name, table_name
), 
volumes AS (  
  SELECT   
    volume_catalog AS catalog_name,  
    volume_owner AS owner,  
    comment,
    last_altered,
    last_altered_by,
    created,
    created_by,
    'volume' AS entity,  
    volume_schema AS schema_name,  
    volume_name,
    '' AS table_name,   
    '' AS data_source_format,  
    '' AS table_type  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.volumes  
),  
volume_tags AS (  
  SELECT   
    volume_name,  
    catalog_name,
    schema_name,
    concat_ws(', ', collect_list(concat(tag_name, ': ', tag_value))) AS tags  
  FROM   
    system.information_schema.volume_tags  
  GROUP BY   
    catalog_name, schema_name, volume_name
),

union_ready_dataset AS (

SELECT   
  c.catalog_name,  
  c.schema_name, 
  c.table_name,  
  c.volume_name, 
  c.owner,  
  c.entity, 
  c.comment,  
  c.last_altered,
  c.last_altered_by,
  c.created,
  c.created_by,
  c.data_source_format,  
  c.table_type,  
  IFNULL(ct.tags, '') AS tags  
FROM   
  catalogs c  
LEFT JOIN   
  catalog_tags ct  
ON   
  c.catalog_name = ct.catalog_name

UNION ALL

SELECT   
  s.catalog_name,  
  s.schema_name, 
  s.table_name,  
  s.volume_name, 
  s.owner,  
  s.entity, 
  s.comment,  
  s.last_altered,
  s.last_altered_by,
  s.created,
  s.created_by,
  s.data_source_format,  
  s.table_type,  
  IFNULL(st.tags, '') AS tags  
FROM   
  schemas s  
LEFT JOIN   
  schema_tags st  
ON   
  s.catalog_name = st.catalog_name AND s.schema_name = st.schema_name

UNION ALL

SELECT   
  t.catalog_name,  
  t.schema_name, 
  t.table_name,  
  t.volume_name, 
  t.owner,  
  t.entity, 
  t.comment,  
  t.last_altered,
  t.last_altered_by,
  t.created,
  t.created_by,
  t.data_source_format,  
  t.table_type,  
  IFNULL(tt.tags, '') AS tags  
FROM   
  tables t  
LEFT JOIN   
  table_tags tt  
ON   
  t.catalog_name = tt.catalog_name AND t.schema_name = tt.schema_name AND t.table_name = tt.table_name

UNION ALL

SELECT   
  v.catalog_name,  
  v.schema_name, 
  v.table_name,  
  v.volume_name, 
  v.owner,  
  v.entity, 
  v.comment,  
  v.last_altered,
  v.last_altered_by,
  v.created,
  v.created_by,
  v.data_source_format,  
  v.table_type,  
  IFNULL(vt.tags, '') AS tags  
FROM   
  volumes v 
LEFT JOIN   
  volume_tags vt  
ON   
  v.catalog_name = vt.catalog_name AND v.schema_name = vt.schema_name AND v.volume_name = vt.volume_name)

SELECT
    catalog_name AS `Catalog name`,
    schema_name AS `Schema name`,
    table_name AS `Table name`,
    volume_name AS `Volume name`,
    owner AS `Owner`,
    comment AS `Comment`,
    tags AS `Tags`,
    entity AS `Entity`,
    last_altered AS `Last Altered`,
    CASE   
        WHEN last_altered >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), 30) THEN '1 month'  
        WHEN last_altered >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), 60) THEN '2 months'  
        WHEN last_altered >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), 120) THEN '4 months'  
        WHEN last_altered >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), 180) THEN '6 months'  
        ELSE 'More than 6 months'  
    END AS ActivityPeriod,  
    last_altered_by AS `Last Altered By`,
    table_type AS `Table Type`,
    data_source_format AS `Data Source Format`,
    created AS `Created`,
    created_by AS `Created By`,
    CASE
      WHEN comment = '' OR comment IS NULL THEN 'No'  
      ELSE 'Yes'
    END AS `Commented`,
    CASE
      WHEN tags = '' OR tags IS NULL THEN 'No'
      ELSE 'Yes'
    END AS `tagged`
FROM 
    union_ready_dataset
WHERE catalog_name != '__databricks_internal' and schema_name != 'information_schema'
AND IF(:param_entity='<ALL>', true, entity = :param_entity)
AND IF(:param_owner='<ALL>', true, owner = :param_owner)
AND IF(:param_catalog_name='<ALL>', true, catalog_name = :param_catalog_name) 
AND IF(:param_schema_name='<ALL>', true, schema_name = :param_schema_name)
AND IF(:param_table_name='<ALL>', true,table_name = :param_table_name)

    schema_name
FROM 
    system.information_schema.schemata
WHERE 
    schema_name NOT LIKE "%__dlt_materialization_schema%"

    AND IF(:param_owner='<ALL>', true, schema_owner = :param_owner)

  v.last_altered_by,
  v.created_by,
  IFNULL(vt.tags, '') AS tags  
FROM   
  volumes v 
LEFT JOIN   
  volume_tags vt  
ON   
  v.catalog_name = vt.catalog_name AND v.schema_name = vt.schema_name AND v.volume_name = vt.volume_name)

SELECT
  COUNT(*) AS `Total Item Count`,  
  SUM(CASE WHEN comment = '' OR comment IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS `Commented Items`,
  SUM(CASE WHEN tags = '' OR tags IS NULL OR tags is NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS `Tagged Items`, 
  ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN comment = '' OR comment IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100,2) AS `Populated Comments (%)`,  
  ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN tags = '' OR tags IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100,2)  AS `Populated Tags (%)`,
  CONCAT(CAST(ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN comment = '' OR comment IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100,2)  AS STRING), '%')   AS `Populated Comments raw (%)`, 
  CONCAT(CAST(ROUND((SUM(CASE WHEN tags = '' OR tags IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) / COUNT(*)) * 100,2)  AS STRING), '%')   AS `Populated Tags raw (%)`
FROM 
    union_ready_dataset
WHERE 
  catalog_name != '__databricks_internal' and schema_name != 'information_schema'
  AND IF(:param_entity='<ALL>', true, entity = :param_entity)
  AND IF(:param_owner='<ALL>', true, owner = :param_owner)
  AND IF(:param_catalog_name='<ALL>', true, catalog_name = :param_catalog_name) 
  AND IF(:param_schema_name='<ALL>', true, schema_name = :param_schema_name)

WITH union_data AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 
    catalog_owner AS owner
FROM 
    system.information_schema.catalogs  

UNION ALL

SELECT DISTINCT 
    schema_owner AS owner
FROM 
    system.information_schema.schemata  

UNION ALL

SELECT DISTINCT 
    table_owner AS owner
FROM 
    system.information_schema.tables

UNION ALL

SELECT DISTINCT 
    volume_owner AS owner
FROM 
    system.information_schema.volumes)

SELECT DISTINCT
    owner
FROM 
    union_data
